category: Devel Libs
requires: cygwin libstatgrab6
external-source: libstatgrab
sdesc: "Make system statistics (development)"
ldesc: "libstatgrab is a library that provides cross platform access to
statistics about the system on which it's run. It's written in C and presents a
selection of useful interfaces which can be used to access key system
statistics. The current list of statistics includes CPU usage, memory
utilisation, disk usage, process counts, network traffic, disk I/O, and more."
